description:
Moves all in-line braces to a new line at the correct indentation level. For example:

func(param){
  // stuff
}
==>>
func(param)
{
  // stuff
}

content:
/*!
	Function: jsonAHK
		Returns an AHK object from a JSON string
	Params:
		s - String representing a JSON object
*/
jsonAHK(s){
	static o:=comobjcreate("scriptcontrol")
	o.language:="jscript"
	return o.eval("(" s ")")
}
